'''Zi-Kree Sector''', or '''Sector 4805''', was one of the many sections of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]-wide city sprawling across the face of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was one of the oldest sections of the city and contained the [[Crimson Corridor]] in its [[Third Quadrant]]. It was located along the equatorial strip of Coruscant. It was located approximately ten kilometers away from the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].<ref name="DM">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]''</ref>

